en revenue, and drawing a multi-product profit-volume chart.\"", "\"HAIR CO'S ELECTRICAL GOODS\":\"Hair Co manufactures three types of electrical goods for hair: curlers (C), straightening irons (S), and dryers (D). The budgeted sales prices and volumes for the next year are provided, along with the standard cost card for each product.\"", "\"RANKING OF PRODUCTS\":\"Ranking of products based on C/S ratio: C is ranked 1, S is ranked 2, and D is ranked 3.\"", "\"MULTI-PRODUCT PV CHART\":\"The multi-product PV chart compares profit against sales revenue for products C, S, and D. It includes a solid line for 'Most profitable first' and a dashed line for 'Constant mix'.\""], "parameters": {"model": "text-embedding-3-small", "temperature": 0.0, "frequency_penalty": null, "presence_penalty": null, "top_p": 1.0, "max_tokens": 4000, "n": 1}}